oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Company B, 306th Ammunition Train song
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This is the lyrics of Co. B, 306th Ammunition Train's unit song. It was written by John S. Collins, presumably a member of the company and relates the history of the unit. This copy belonged to Pvt. Emmett L. Moorer of Henning, Lauderdale County, Tennessee.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: World War, 1914-1918; World War, 1914-1918 - History
